column5: Has anybody been to Populous Lake? Canada Outfitters out of Kenora. An outpost camp. How was it? How was the outfitter?
I haven't fished Populus, but I can attest to the fact that they are a great outfitter.Frank
Agree with Breezy, outfitter is wonderful. His camp and equipment on Gordie Lake was way too nice for an outpost. Please report when you return!
